==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outsell
<hw>Out*sell"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
exceed in amount of sales; to sell more than.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To exceed in the price of selling; to fetch more
than; to exceed in value.</def> <rj><au>Fuller.</au>
<au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outsentry</ent>⟦br⟧
